text: Sonam Chuki (born 7 April 1963), is a former Bhutanese archer who internationally represented Bhutan. Chuki competed for Bhutan at the 1984 Summer Olympics held in Los Angeles in the individual event where she finished 43rd.Sports Reference Profile ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic archers of Bhutan Category:Archers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Bhutanese female archers
